txt.en: Orkish siege engines can be found in Harlond.\n\nYou should destroy these siege engines before the Rammas is toppled by the Orkish forces gathered in Harlond.
'The Morgul troops in the Harlond have constructed metal siege weapons. We must destroy these abominations before they tear down the Rammas!'
Orkish siege engines can be found in the Harlond.\n\nYou should destroy these siege engines before the Rammas is toppled by the Orkish forces gathered in the Harlond.
Aragorn will need the port of the Harlond cleared if he and his men are to make landfall with haste.
